data.description: ASSUMABLE 3.5% FHA LOAN!!!! Here is your chance to grab a LOW INTEREST RATE and achieve homeownership! This nearly new condo is conveniently located on the middle level and built in 2018. Complete with open concept layout, quartz countertops and stainless appliances. Primary bedroom includes a private bathroom and walk-in closet. Quick access to stores, restaurants, trailheads, parks, and Blackridge Pond Reservoir. Don't miss this opportunity to grab a low interest rate and own a home!  All information deemed accurate and reliable.  Buyer to verify all.
